---
title: Honey-Glazed Haloumi & Spiced Veggie Toss with Almonds & Mayo
description: Here’s a hearty vegetarian meal that brings inspiration from across the globe to your plate. Flavourful haloumi meets
roasted vegetables tossed with Tunisian-style spices, plus there’s toasted almonds to finish it off.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/honey-glazed-haloumi-spiced-roast-veggies-65f0f25c.jpg
